        Ao registar o seu espaço na secção seguinte desta página, receberá um
        KIT que inclui:
      </p>

      <ul class="ml-80 xl:ml-0 mt-56 text-28 space-y-56 xl:text-20 md:text-16">
        <li
          class="flex flex-row items-start space-x-24 sm:flex-col sm:space-x-0 sm:space-y-16"
        >
          <svg
            style="min-width: 54px"
            width="54"
            height="54"
            viewBox="0 0 55 55"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="transform -translate-y-4 xl:-translate-y-1/4"
          >
            <circle cx="27.2006" cy="27.2006" r="27.2006" fill="#FF3838" />
          </svg>

          <p>
            um autocolante para colocar na porta, por forma a ser reconhecido
            como um membro da comunidade pão no gancho;
          </p>
        </li>

        <li
          class="flex flex-row items-start space-x-24 sm:flex-col sm:space-x-0 sm:space-y-16"
        >
          <svg
            style="min-width: 54px"
            width="54"
            height="54"
            viewBox="0 0 54 56"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="transform -translate-y-4 xl:-translate-y-1/4"
          >
            <path
              d="M22.2347 2.95051C24.9043 0.231304 29.2854 0.231304 31.9549 2.95051C33.5133 4.53786 35.7486 5.26417 37.9424 4.89596C41.7004 4.26519 45.2448 6.84033 45.8061 10.6093C46.1339 12.8095 47.5154 14.711 49.5066 15.7026C52.9177 17.4012 54.2715 21.5678 52.5103 24.947C51.4822 26.9196 51.4822 29.27 52.5103 31.2426C54.2715 34.6218 52.9177 38.7884 49.5066 40.487C47.5154 41.4786 46.1339 43.3801 45.8061 45.5803C45.2448 49.3493 41.7004 51.9244 37.9424 51.2937C35.7486 50.9254 33.5133 51.6517 31.9549 53.2391C29.2854 55.9583 24.9043 55.9583 22.2347 53.2391C20.6764 51.6517 18.441 50.9254 16.2473 51.2937C12.4892 51.9244 8.94486 49.3493 8.38347 45.5803C8.05575 43.3801 6.67423 41.4786 4.68301 40.487C1.27196 38.7884 -0.0818758 34.6218 1.67931 31.2426C2.70741 29.27 2.70741 26.9196 1.67931 24.947C-0.0818758 21.5678 1.27196 17.4012 4.68301 15.7026C6.67423 14.711 8.05575 12.8095 8.38347 10.6093C8.94486 6.84033 12.4892 4.26519 16.2473 4.89596C18.441 5.26417 20.6764 4.53786 22.2347 2.95051Z"
              fill="#4355FF"
            />
          </svg>

          <p>o gancho solidário;</p>
        </li>

        <li
          class="flex flex-row items-start space-x-24 sm:flex-col sm:space-x-0 sm:space-y-16"
        >
          <svg
            style="min-width: 54px"
            width="54"
            height="54"
            viewBox="0 0 54 53"
